âš™ï¸ How It Works

User logs into the system.

Monthly data such as electricity usage, fuel consumption, and food expenses are entered.

Carbon emissions are calculated using predefined emission factors.

The system generates:

Total Carbon Footprint

Sustainability Score

AI-based suggestions

Historical data is stored in SQLite.

A Machine Learning model predicts next month's emissions.

Leaderboard ranks users based on lowest emissions.

